ofxGLEditor (for live coding)

The main functionarities and sources are taken from awesome fluxus.
http://www.pawfal.org/fluxus/

clipboards are form here
http://forum.openframeworks.cc/index.php?topic=2296.0

ofxGLEditor needs ofxKeyMap
http://forum.openframeworks.cc/index.php?topic=2034.0
http://companje.nl/downloads/openframeworks/ofxKeyMap.zip

and needs Monospaced font.

USAGE:
### testApp.h ###
#include "ofxGLEditor.h"
ofxGLEditor ofeditor;

### testApp.cpp ###
void testApp::setup(){
	ofBackground(0);
	ofeditor.setup();

	// if you have some script lang companion (e.g. ofxLua)	
	//ofAddListener(ofeditor.doCompileEvent, this, &yourClass::yourListener);
}

void testApp::draw(){
	ofeditor.draw();
}

void testApp::keyPressed(int key){
	bool alt = ofeditor.isAltPressed();
	if (alt && key == 'f') {
		ofToggleFullscreen();
		ofeditor.reShape();
	}
	ofeditor.keyPressed(key);
}